{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/DOTFLFaceAutoCaptureConfigurationPresets\/simple"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration suitable for face verification use cases."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The component operates without any visual aids or guidance for the user, with the exception of the detection layer (tracking circle)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There is no automatic triggering of the capture process."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Instead, the client is responsible for initiating the capture by explicitly calling the "},{"type":"text","text":"requestCapture"},{"type":"text","text":" method."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This configuration provides a minimalistic approach, offering flexibility to the client in managing the capture timing and user interaction,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which is often desired in verification scenarios."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite","doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/DOTFLFaceAutoCaptureConfigurationPresets"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"strong"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DOTFLFaceAutoCaptureConfiguration","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@DotFaceLite@objc(cs)DOTFLFaceAutoCaptureConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/DOTFLFaceAutoCaptureConfiguration"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"simple"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["